  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Vale.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Vale and the location of Redfort\"><img alt=\"The Vale and the location of Redfort\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/29/The_Vale.png/400px-The_Vale.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/29/The_Vale.png/600px-The_Vale.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/29/The_Vale.png/800px-The_Vale.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 72.2%; left: 59.2%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -8px; top: -8px; width: 15px; font-size: 15px;\"><img alt=\"The Vale and the location of Redfort\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Redfort\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/23px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/30px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Redfort</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale</a> and the location of Redfort\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Redfort</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> also called <b>the Redfort</b>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> is the ancient seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Redfort\" title=\"House Redfort\">House Redfort</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Vale_of_Arryn\" title=\"Vale of Arryn\">Vale of Arryn</a>. It is located in the south of the valley. It is southeast of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>, south of <a href=\"/index.php/Ironoaks\" title=\"Ironoaks\">Ironoaks</a>, and north of <a href=\"/index.php/Wickenden\" title=\"Wickenden\">Wickenden</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Redfort&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> visited Redfort during a <a href=\"/index.php/Royal_progress\" title=\"Royal progress\">royal progress</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/52_AC\" title=\"52 AC\">52&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabbirth.2C_death.2C_and_betrayal_under_king_jaehaerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Redfort&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=